OL,3,CMinister says she will 'sort out' HS2
OL,4,Cand confirms opening will be delayed
OL,6,FA minister has pledged to "sort out"
OL,7,Fthe "appalling mess" of HS2 and
OL,8,Fconfirmed the railway's opening will
OL,9,Fbe further delayed.
OL,11,FTransport Secretary Heidi Alexander
OL,12,Ftold the Commons there is "no route"
OL,13,Fto meet the target date of having HS2
OL,14,Fservices running by 2033.
OL,16,FThe project has suffered repeated
OL,17,Fdelays and soaring costs despite being
OL,18,Fscaled back.
OL,20,FMs Alexander said: "It's an appalling
OL,21,Fmess, but it's one we will sort out.
