OL,6,F"We need to set targets which we can
OL,7,Fconfidently deliver, that the public
OL,8,Fcan trust, and that will take time.
OL,10,F"But rest assured, where there are
OL,11,Finefficiencies, we will root them out."
OL,13,FThe Cabinet minister said an interim
OL,14,Freport by Mark Wild, the chief
OL,15,Fexecutive of HS2 Ltd, who was
OL,16,Fappointed late last year, "lays bare
OL,17,Fthe shocking mismanagement of the
OL,18,Fproject under previous governments".
