OL,6,FShe added: "He stated, in no uncertain
OL,7,Fterms, the overall project with
OL,8,Frespect of cost, schedule and scope is
OL,9,Funsustainable.
OL,11,F"Based on his advice, I see no route
OL,12,Fby which trains can be running by 2033
OL,13,Fas planned.
OL,15,F"He reveals costs will continue to
OL,16,Fincrease if not taken in hand, further
OL,17,Foutstripping the budget set by the
OL,18,Fprevious government.
