OL,4,Cand confirms opening will be delayed
OL,6,F"We won't reinstate cancelled sections
OL,7,Fwe can't afford, but we will do the
OL,8,Fhard but necessary work to rebuild
OL,9,Fpublic trust."
OL,11,FHS2 was originally due to run between
OL,12,FLondon and Birmingham, then on to
OL,13,FManchester and Leeds, but the project
OL,14,Fwas severely curtailed by the
OL,15,FConservatives in power because of
OL,16,Fspiralling costs.
OL,18,FThe first phase was initially planned
OL,19,Fto open by the end of 2026, but this
OL,20,Fwas pushed back to between 2029 and
OL,21,F2033.
